cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: FCL031F - Multi Supplier Framework Agreement for the provision of Commercial Cleaning and Window Cleaning Services
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: The Contracting Authority invites tenders (“Tenders”) from economic operators (“Tenderers”) for appointment to a multi-supplier framework agreement (the “Framework Agreement”) for the provision of the services as described in Appendix 1 and Appendix 9 to this RFT (the “Services”). In summary, the Services comprise of Commercial and Window Cleaning Services throughout the State.
